'''越南更新革命党'''（{{lang-vi|Việt Nam Canh Tân Cách Mạng Đảng}}），简称'''越新'''（{{lang-vi|Việt Tân}}），是一个在[[越南|越南]]境内秘密活动以及在越南国外活动的政党，其目的是以和平和政治手段在对越南进行改革，建立[[民主|民主]]制度。<ref name="senate.gov">{{cite web|url=http://www.senate.gov/~foreign/testimony/2008/DiemTestimony080312p.pdf|format=PDF|title=Testimony before the Senate Foreign Relations Committee Subcommittee on East Asian and Pacific Affairs|accessdate=2008-05-07|date=2008-03-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502193956/http://www.senate.gov/~foreign/testimony/2008/DiemTestimony080312p.pdf|archivedate=2008-05-02|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="AlistairCommendsVietTan">{{cite web|url=http://www.alistaircoe.com.au/2009/viet-tan/|title=Alistair commends Vietnam pro-democracy movement|author=Alistair Coe|accessdate=2009-12-06|date=2009-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903181004/http://www.alistaircoe.com.au/2009/viet-tan/|archive-date=2011-09-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

越新的前身是1980年4月30日由前[[南越海军|南越海军]][[准將|准將]][[黃機明|黃機明]]建立的[[越南国家统一解放阵线|越南国家统一解放阵线]]（{{vie|qn=Mặt trận Quốc gia Thống nhất Giải phóng Việt Nam|hn=𩈘陣國家統一解放越南}}），该组织曾在地下活跃二十年之久。2004年9月19日，继任主席[[阮金|阮金]]解散了这个组织，改组为越南更新革命党并延续至今。<ref name="ReasonsPublicVietTan">{{cite web|url=http://www.viettan.org/article.php3?id_article=830|title=Reasons for the Public Introduction of Viet Tan|author=Kim Nguyen|accessdate=2008-05-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061014064035/http://www.viettan.org/article.php3?id_article=830|archivedate=2006-10-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

越新目前被越南当局列为[[非法政党|非法政党]]和[[恐怖组织|恐怖组织]]，<ref name = thayer>{{cite web|url=http://johnib.wordpress.com/tag/viet-tan/|title=Background Briefing: Viet Tan|author=Carlyle A. Thayer|accessdate=2007-08-03|date=2007-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070718120233/http://johnib.wordpress.com/tag/viet-tan/|archive-date=2007-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name = TehranTimes>{{cite web|url=http://johnib.wordpress.com/tag/viet-tan/|title=Pro-reform party coddled in U.S|accessdate=2008-04-15|date=2007-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070718120233/http://johnib.wordpress.com/tag/viet-tan/|archive-date=2007-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>然而事实上越新的成员们一直致力以非暴力手段来改变越南。<ref name="senate.gov"/><ref name="HumanRightsWatchReleaseConvictedActivists">{{cite web|url=http://www.hrw.org/news/2013/01/09/vietnam-release-convicted-activists|title=Vietnam: Release Convicted Activists - Drop Charges Against Blogger Le Quoc Quan|date=2013-01-09|publisher=Human Rights Watch|accessdate=19 July 2012|archive-date=2015-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150807153628/http://www.hrw.org/news/2013/01/09/vietnam-release-convicted-activists|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年[[美国政府|美国政府]]也承认没有任何证据显示越新有任何与恐怖组织相似的罪恶行径，<ref name="FoxNewsVietnamArrestsApril2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/04/29/vietnam-arrests-us-pro-democracy-activist/|accessdate=2012-05-02|work=Associated Press|date=2012-04-29|title=Vietnam arrests US pro-democracy activist|archive-date=2012-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502004328/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/04/29/vietnam-arrests-us-pro-democracy-activist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>并认为越新是一个“提倡民主改革的和平组织”。<ref name="UnitedNationsConcerned">{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=43906&Cr=vietnam&Cr1=|title=UN human rights office concerned over convictions of 14 activists in Vietnam|accessdate=2013-01-11|date=2013-01-11|publisher=United Nations|archive-date=2013-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116084453/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=43906&Cr=vietnam&Cr1=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

